name: Data Scientists_JUN.2023
description: The Data Scientist Collection represents the skills necessary for professionals responsible for transforming raw data into useful information by developing and implementing techniques or analytics applications. It includes data mining, data modeling, and machine learning skills. This collection of skills was developed in partnership with a panel of subject matter experts who have worked as data scientists.
